{"tid":644441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[No IT]傳美擬收緊中美企業合作審查　劍指AI","createTime":"2018-04-27T08:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T09:11:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd22b3f4aba609de076380f3b32f125844a4649","tid":644441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"電引述消息報道，美國政府擬審查中美企業在人工智能(AI)方面的合作，目前監控範圍以投資、併購為主，未來可能擴大至非正式夥伴關係，如研究實驗室、頂尖人才交流等。<br />\n<br />\n是次AI受到關注，消息指，是因為有關技術可能運用到軍事上；另半導體、自動駕駛汽車等亦有機會受到審查。<br />\n<br />\n據4名消息人士指，建議擴大審查是由部分議員和美國總統特朗普政府的部分官員提出，他們憂慮知識產權被竊取及技術被轉讓至中國。<br />\n<br />\n美國大型科企包括<span style=\"color: red;\">高通、英偉達、AMD、IBM等均有於中國設研究實驗室等</span>，目前AI和晶片設計等人才可於兩國的各企業和大學之間自由流動。是次美國政府擬進行審查，可能對整體行業構成極大影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180427/bkn-20180427153123151-0427_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180427%2Fbkn-20180427153123151-0427_00842_001.html&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=dfabcde9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180427/bkn-20180427153123151-0427_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8da9bf9b5fb2cadfc870978a730e27f0179d2e85","tid":644441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"world no IT"},{"pid":"e822aaa8ed67fdec78b4a0931a1258d5a61dd3ab","tid":644441,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"CHI NA NO IT"},{"pid":"f2b8e0d453b410db14fdc874c8d6231cf7e4706e","tid":644441,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"ai is dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec907b4b24ac278edf1dc27249b8134e0edad94","tid":644441,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b8e0d453b410db14fdc874c8d6231cf7e4706e","tid":644441,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"